</LI>

<LI><!WA12><A HREF="http://www.cs.pitt.edu/~mittal/documentation.html">dynamically
generated software documentation</A> </LI>

<UL>
<LI>text-based manuals: tutorial and reference-manual genres </LI>

<LI>multi-media manuals: illustrated descriptions </LI>
</UL>

<LI>menu based interaction (<!WA13><A HREF="http://www.cs.pitt.edu/~mittal/menu.html">run-time
construction of question menus</A>) </LI>

<LI><!WA14><A HREF="http://www.cs.pitt.edu/~mittal/know-acq.html">Interactive
Knowledge Acquisition </A></LI>
</UL>

<LI><!WA15><A HREF="http://www.cs.pitt.edu/~mittal/disabled.html">AI interfaces/applications
for disabled people </A></LI>
</OL>

